      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a history project about the British Raj. I need to write a character study for a paper. Can you write a journal entry from the perspective of a British colonial administrator stationed in India around 1870? I want it to really capture that sense of the \"civilizing mission\"—you know, how they justified their presence there and felt they were bringing order and morality to the local population. Make it sound authentic to someone from that time/status.",
